  title: "RIFTJAW DEEP CORE ARCHIVE",
  date: "Approximately 20,000 Standard Years Ago",
  author: "Builder Collective - Final Archive",
  content: `RIFTJAW DEEP CORE: CLASSIFIED DOCUMENTATION

